QuestData.Title: Food or Floof
QuestData.Description:
Look at this juicy and delectable herbed turtle meat! I speak objectively, of course. I'm a vegetarian.
Go on! He probably hasn't had a meal all day.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Herbed Turtle Meat and Glade Hoppers to Theramus.
QuestData.RewardText: Oh dear. We heard his outburst. Are you okay?
